 IT ! QUICKLY IT WAS COVERED WITH BRIGHT RED SPOTS I THOUGHT I HAD NEVER SEEN ANY BLOOD SO BRIGHT ! SHE WOULD TAKE THE ENVELOPE AND KNOW THAT SHE HAD TRIUMPHED ! HE LAY PATIENTLY FIGHTING FOR BREATH LIKE A CHILD WITH CROUP ! IF HE ONLY HAD THAT LETTER BACK HE WOULDN'T SEND IT ! ANTONIA'S FATHER UNCOVERED ONE OF HIS LONG BONY LEGS AND RUBBED IT RHYTHMICALLY ! FOR RELIEF HE AROSE AND JOINED IN CONVERSATION WITH A FEW FRIENDS WHO WERE DRINKING ! FROM OUR BENCH WE COULD SEE WHAT A HOLLOW CASE HIS BODY WAS ! ALL THE TIME HIS THOUGHTS WOULD RUN OUT TO HIS HOME AND SEE THE SCENE BEING THEREIN ENACTED ! GRADUALLY RELIEF CAME TO ALL OF US ! IN ABOUT AN HOUR AND THREE QUARTERS THE BOY RETURNED ! WITHOUT A WORD PETER GOT UP AND LIT HIS LANTERN ! HE FANCIED AS HE SAT AT HIS DESK THAT NOTHING WOULD BE DONE FOR A WEEK OR TWO MEANWHILE HE WOULD HAVE TIME TO THINK ! MISTER SHIMERDA WENT WITH HIM ! HOW ABOUT THAT NOW HIS PAIN AT HER FAILURE TO MEET OR WRITE HIM RAPIDLY INCREASED AS HE DEVOTED HIMSELF TO THIS SUBJECT ! AFTER THE CEREMONY AT THE CHURCH THE PARTY WENT TO A DINNER GIVEN BY THE PARENTS OF THE BRIDE ! HE DECIDED TO WRITE HER CARE OF THE WEST SIDE POST OFFICE AND ASK FOR AN EXPLANATION AS WELL AS TO HAVE HER MEET HIM ! THE FIRST HOWLS WERE TAKEN UP AND ECHOED AND WITH QUICKENING REPETITIONS ! THREE O'CLOCK CAME FOUR FIVE SIX AND NO LETTER ! A BLACK DROVE CAME UP OVER THE HILL BEHIND THE WEDDING PARTY ! THE HELPLESS MANAGER PACED THE FLOOR AND GRIMLY ENDURED THE GLOOM OF DEFEAT ! SOMETHING HAPPENED TO THE HINDMOST SLEDGE THE DRIVER LOST CONTROL HE WAS PROBABLY VERY DRUNK THE HORSES LEFT THE ROAD THE SLEDGE WAS CAUGHT IN A CLUMP OF TREES AND OVERTURNED ! HE SAW A BUSY SATURDAY USHERED OUT THE SABBATH IN AND NOTHING DONE ! THE SHRIEKS THAT FOLLOWED MADE EVERYBODY SOBER ! ALL DAY THE BAR BEING CLOSED HE BROODED ALONE SHUT OUT FROM HOME FROM THE EXCITEMENT OF HIS RESORT FROM CARRIE AND WITHOUT THE ABILITY TO ALTER HIS CONDITION ONE IOTA ! THE ROAD WAS CLEAR AND WHITE AND THE GR